      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COOL RUPEE (6) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 9 lengths at this track in a handy 31.11 beating CARUGGI. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. ADHANA LULU (2) produced a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 525m behind Raven Peter (32.08) in a NG. Was in the money the start prior. One of the main contenders. CARUGGI (3) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished in the money last time though when second (31.77) at this track. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Can measure up. TAZ MANIAC (1) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can atone.",
